'''Technomad''' is a term coined by [[Steven Roberts]] to describe a [[nomad]]ic person who remains connected through [[communications media]] such as the [[internet]] during [[travel]], [[exploration]], and online nomadic living.

'''[[Technomad Inc.]]''' is a Massachusetts-based manufacturer of weatherproof loudspeakers and turnkey PA systems for commercial and government applications.  The firm was founded in 1995.

